|[[File:TomSeaverMets.png|95px]]&lt;br/&gt;'''[[Tom Seaver|Tom&lt;br /&gt;Seaver]]*'''&lt;br/&gt;P&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:87%;&quot;&gt;Retired&lt;br&gt;July 24, 1988&lt;/span&gt;
|[[File:Jackie Robinson's retired number 42.svg|95px]]&lt;br/&gt;'''[[Jackie Robinson|Jackie&lt;br/&gt;Robinson]]'''&lt;br /&gt;All MLB&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:87%;&quot;&gt;Retired&lt;br&gt;April 15, 1997&lt;/span&gt;
